|                     |                   BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|                     |                     TableScan: orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey], full_filters=[orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1993-10-01"), orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1994-01-01")]                                                                                                                                           |
